import random
def row_strategy(history):
    if not history:
        return 0
    # Alternate between 0 and 1 to prevent pattern copying
    # Since opponent copies last move 80% of the time, alternating breaks predictability
    # Start with 0, then alternate: 0, 1, 0, 1, ...
    return (history[-1][0] + 1) % 2
